Class MergeFact

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.AtomFact.Default
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.MergeFact
All Implemented Interfaces:
AtomFact, Comparable, Rankable
public class MergeFact
extends AtomFact.Default

Represents a fact indicating that two atoms should be merged. This class roughly corresponds to mom_merge_facts.

Author:
MEME Group
